<h1 id="content">Logger.h</h1>
<article>

    <p id="articleTitle">File Description</p>
    <p id="article">
        This header allows for easier access to the I/O systems in the NXT file system and can log 
        various data types into a human readable text document.
    </p>

    <p id="article">
        Only members which are meant to be accessed, called, or started in the cases of fields, met
        hods, and tasks, respectively, are shown, some members may be excluded.
    </p>

</article>

